statements: SELECT user_id, page_visited, timestamp, duration_sec FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT page_visited, timestamp, duration_sec, user_id FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT user_id, duration_sec, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT page_visited, user_id, duration_sec, timestamp FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT timestamp, user_id, duration_sec, page_visited FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT user_id, page_visited, timestamp, duration_sec FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY user_id ASC, timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT user_id, SUM(duration_sec) AS total_duration FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY total_duration DESC
SELECT user_id, page_visited, timestamp FROM website_traffic_data WHERE duration_sec > 60 AND page_visited LIKE '%home%' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS unique_users, AVG(duration_sec) AS avg_duration FROM website_traffic_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28'
SELECT user_id, page_visited, duration_sec FROM website_traffic_data WHERE duration_sec > (SELECT AVG(duration_sec) FROM website_traffic_data) ORDER BY duration_sec DESC, user_id ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT page_url, page_views FROM website_traffic_data WHERE date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT user_id, page_views FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY page_views DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_engagement WHERE total_sessions > 10;
SELECT user_id, email, last_activity_date FROM user_engagement WHERE sign_up_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY date DESC, time_spent ASC;
SELECT user_id, page_url, page_views FROM website_traffic_data WHERE page_views > 100;
SELECT DISTINCT(user_id) FROM website_traffic_data WHERE page_views >= 50;
SELECT user_id, total_sessions FROM user_engagement WHERE last_activity_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY total_sessions DESC;
SELECT page_url, SUM(page_views) AS total_page_views FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY page_url HAVING total_page_views > 500;
SELECT * FROM website_visits;
SELECT user_id, page_url FROM website_visits WHERE device_type = 'mobile';
SELECT page_url, unique_visitors, avg_engagement_time FROM page_data ORDER BY unique_visitors DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_activity WHERE total_visits > 100 AND total_engagement_time > INTERVAL '1 hour';
SELECT user_id, last_login FROM user_activity ORDER BY last_login DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_visits;
SELECT user_id, page_url, visit_timestamp FROM website_visits WHERE device_type='mobile' ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT page_url, COUNT(visit_id) AS visit_count FROM website_visits GROUP BY page_url HAVING COUNT(visit_id) > 10 ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id, total_visits, total_engagement_time FROM user_activity WHERE total_visits > 100 ORDER BY total_visits DESC, total_engagement_time ASC;
SELECT page_url, unique_visitors, (unique_visitors / total_visits) * 100 AS conversion_rate FROM page_data ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC, unique_visitors DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_visits;
SELECT visitor_id, visit_date, page_visited FROM website_visits WHERE visit_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, age, gender, location FROM visitor_demographics WHERE age > 30;
SELECT view_id, page_id, time_on_page FROM page_views ORDER BY time_on_page DESC;
SELECT visit_id, clicked_element, click_timestamp FROM click_events WHERE interaction_type = 'button';
SELECT * FROM website_visits ORDER BY visit_date ASC, visitor_id DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT visitor_id, visit_duration FROM website_visits WHERE visit_id = 100 AND page_visited = 'homepage';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_visits, AVG(visit_duration) AS average_duration FROM website_visits WHERE visit_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT visitor_id, age, location, device_used FROM visitor_demographics WHERE age > 25 AND gender = 'Male';
SELECT page_id, SUM(scroll_depth) AS total_scroll_depth FROM page_views GROUP BY page_id HAVING SUM(scroll_depth) > 100;
SELECT * FROM website_users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM website_users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT username, email FROM website_users WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT * FROM page_views ORDER BY view_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_views FROM page_views GROUP BY user_id;

SELECT username, email, registration_date FROM website_users WHERE user_id = 1
SELECT page_name, view_date FROM page_views ORDER BY view_date DESC
